    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos vir
                        gloriosissimus <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps"
                            >Sichardus</persName> Dei previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus Dei omnipotentis misericordia, pro
                        redemptione anime nostre seu gentis et patrie, suggerente potestatis nostre
                            <rs key="#Personal_rank">viro venerabili</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/192" key="#Prevosts">Bassaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85" key="#Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> sito
                        infra hanc Beneventanam civitatem nostram, <rs key="#Intercessory">per
                            rogum</rs>
                        <name ref="Azo">Ationi</name> dilecto cognato nostro, concedimus in prephato
                        Beate Sophie cenobio, ub <persName ref="#people/3461" key="#Abbesses"
                            >Wilerona</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> preesse videtur, ipsa <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >curte</rs> sacri nostri palatii de loco <placeName ref="#places/3480"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Gualdi #Fiscal_property"
                            >Leone Cobante</placeName> cum integro ipso <rs key="#Gualdi"
                            >gualdo</rs> ubi ipsa Cerbareze dicitur, quod est <rs key="#Size"
                            >miliaria duo in longitudo et in latitudo miliaria duo</rs>. In integra
                        ipsa curte cum eodem gualdo in eodem monasterio ipso concessimus, in ea
                        videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceph per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum
                        cuncta que prelegitur ipsum monasterium et eiusque rectores securo nomine
                        habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus abeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3462" key="#Writer">Theodericus</persName>. Actum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName>
                        feliciter primo anno, mense aprili, undecima indictione.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
